window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>They locked up a healer. What came out was something far more dangerous.</b></p> <p>Doctor Ethan Bishop has been exposed. Since arriving on Nexum, he’s gained power and enemies in equal measure. Healing a dying friend put him in the Church’s crosshairs, and now he’s paying the price.<br> <br> But Ethan isn’t done fighting. To uncover the Church’s secrets he’ll make any sacrifice, even if it means fighting under the banner of his greatest enemy.<br> <br> Ethan is certain that the truth lies in the ruins of the Forgotten City. To survive the journey, he must evolve faster than ever and drag his allies into a war they didn’t ask for. What waits in the ruins could change everything… or destroy what’s left.<br> <br> The Assassin is unleashed, and he’s not just taking back what’s his. He’s taking everything.</p>"; 
